{"tid":196744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好心D仆街消防家屬學下人地女報販啦！","createTime":"2017-04-11T13:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T14:44:33.000Z","uid":83060,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fba84ff3953362a2cf2367e63bbadd2159e02447","tid":196744,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"【淒涼報檔】兩張萬元支票  女報販：轉交慈善機構 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆竊事件發生後，報檔女東主蔣小姐，得到很多熱心人士支持，<span style=\"color: red;\">昨天還收到兩張分別1萬6千元的支票，合共3萬2千元，兩張支票將會轉交慈善機構，她表示「多謝個的鼓勵我同支持我的好人，我會加油繼續好好生活下去，呢件事之後有咁多支持同幫助，唔好再嚟捐錢畀我喇。」</span>她稱想自食其力平靜地生活下去。 <br />\n <br />\n平日負責替蔣小姐疊報紙的林婆婆表示，「我覺得佢真係好慘，佢老公醫咗好多錢，一下就去咗！原本我諗住退休唔做㗎啦，佢老公死咗無幾耐，諗下諗下，睇到佢咁淒涼，幫吓佢啦，做報紙呢行人工唔多好難搵人㗎。」 <br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170411&amp;guid=56548849&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170411%26guid%3D56548849%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=69afb182\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170411%26guid%3D56548849%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=2f2e0dec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170411&amp;guid=56548849&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"107d50e29014986889ec66183d1de73bc62cd9d6","tid":196744,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"成千萬，比我都唔退喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1ef93ab43c44ad3d4ef5fa56c2c5363b176533","tid":196744,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"屌你 支票唔用咪算囉 攞去益d慈善組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f949f4870d26947fc6248095a862672757f12a4c","tid":196744,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0